modules.description: This module converts between lambda streams and Lwt values, lists, and streams. It provides functions to extract the first or last value from a stream as a promise, collect all values into a list, and interoperate with Lwt streams. Concrete use cases include handling asynchronous data from network sources or event streams using Lwt's concurrency model.
